   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"(Christian sign) A bag of bread. a flask of vinegar, two baskets of wine, four xestes of oil, a measure of olives; give them to this man who will come to you.";(Verso): (Christian sign) "Brother George to Victor."</ab>
